Dear Sir,

We are one of the well established company in Bangladesh.
Now, we are looking for a reliable and flexible Insurance/Risk Management Company to make business collaboration to work in Bangladesh.

Tradings we are with:

# Agricultural Commodities Export worldwide.
# Garments Apparel Export worldwide.
# Software Development and IT Soluction.
# Online Newspaper in Bangladesh.
# Nationwide Chain Shop.

Our Capabilities, we have studied:

# Covered network in all over export trading companies in Bangladesh, as we are doing several export trade too for a long time with good reputation.
# Expended network with direct public market, as we are operating several public medias and trades.
# Faster networking market growth experience.

Prospects in Bangladesh of Insurance Industry, we have studied:

# As Bangladesh is an export based country in Apparel, Agricultural, Natural Resources etc. Shipping Cargo Insurance has a vast market.
# As Bangladesh is an import based country in Automobile, Telecommunications etc. Shipping Cargo Insurance has a vast market.
# As Bangladesh is a large populated developing country, people's life insurance has a huge market.

As we followed our huge chain network through all over Bangladesh, we are very much confident to make a good business market in INSURANCE/RISK MANAGEMENT Industry here.
So that, we are looking for a reliable and well established company to be their corporate agent in Bangladesh.

If you are interested to make a business collaboration as per we mentioned above, please, reply us with your company profile, offers and services documents, terms and conditions documents and other necessary documents to let us understand your details.

Please, do not hesitate for any kind of inquiry.

Hope to get earlier and fruitful response from you soon.

Email: bd.insurance@yahoo.com
